Package: typstable
Title: Create Typst Tables from Data Frames
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Filip", "", , email = "author@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generate Typst table markup from tibbles and data.frames with
    kableExtra-like styling capabilities. Supports column/row/cell formatting,
    data-driven styling, math equations, and seamless Quarto integration.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
